        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Half-day turnaround</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Most straight replacements start and finish in a single half-day visit, so your basement isn't opened up for days at a time.</p>
