        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Code compliance built in</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Every replacement meets current egress code for opening size, sill height, and clear width, which matters for safety and for future home sales.</p>
